# FlareSolverr + Screenshot DLC

FlareSolverr: FlareSolverr is a proxy server that bypasses Cloudflare and DDoS-GUARD protection
(FlareSolverr 是绕过 Cloudflare 和 DDoS-GUARD 保护的代理服务器)

Screenshot DLC: Add the function of getting screenshots of websites based on FlareSolverr
(在FlareSolverr基础上增加获取网站截图功能)

## Install - 安装

Consistent with the original FlareSolverr  
(与原版FlareSolverr一致)

## Usage - 用法

> As with the original FlareSolverr, only the new screenshot command usage is described here  
(与原版FlareSolverr一致，这里仅介绍新增的截图命令用法)

Example screenshot command request - (示例截图命令请求):
```bash
curl -L -X POST 'http://localhost:8191/v1' \
-H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{
  "cmd": "request.get",
  "url":"https://baidu.com/",
  "returnScreenshot":true,
  "screenshotOption":{"type":"jpeg","resolution":"2k"},
  "maxTimeout": 80000
}'
```
return - (返回)  
![](.github/1.png)

The `screenshot` under `solution` returns a base64-valued image, and you can get the image by writing a good conversion on your own backend  
(其中 `solution` 下的 `screenshot` 返回的是base64值的图像，自己后端写好转换就可以得到图片)
### Command - 命令



#### + `request.get`

> As with the original FlareSolverr, only the new screenshot command usage is described here  
(与原版FlareSolverr一致，这里仅介绍新增的截图命令用法)

Parameter(命令) | Notes(说明)
|--|--|
returnScreenshot | Boolean value indicating whether to output the screenshot (output as a `base64` screenshot), default is `false`  (布尔值，表示是否输出截图(输出为`base64`的截图)，默认为 `false`)
screenshotOption | `json` dictionary format, parameters for generating screenshots, `optional` (json字典格式，生成截图的参数，`可选`)

The full format of `screenshotOption` is as follows, where the four keys in the json can be filled in or not, not filled is the default value as follows  
(`screenshotOption` 完整格式如下，其中json内的四个key可填可不填，不填就是如下的默认值。)

```json
{
    "resolution": "1080p",
    "type": "png",
    "quality": 100,
    "fullPage": false
}

```
`screenshotOption` format description - (`screenshotOption` 格式说明)
Parameter(命令) | Notes(说明)
|--|--|
resolution | Resolution, optional `720p`, `1080p`, `2k` (分辨率，可选`720p`，`1080p`，`2k`)
type | Image type, optionally `png`, `jpeg`(图片类型，可选`png`，`jpeg`)
quality | Image quality, only available if `image type` is `jpeg` (图片质量，仅当 `图片类型` 为 `jpeg` 时可用)
fullPage | Whether to intercept the full page, have not tried (是否截取完整页面，没试过)
